-!- FUNCTION: Required for the activity of the bacterial periplasmic
    transport system of putrescine and spermidine. Polyamine binding
    protein (By similarity).
-!- SUBCELLULAR LOCATION: Periplasm (By similarity).
-!- SIMILARITY: Belongs to the bacterial solute-binding protein
    potD/potF family.
